# Button navigation (Control Pane)

- For in-app navigation, use **React Router** `Link` (or `NavLink`) instead of buttons that only call `navigate()` without a real link, when you want right-click / open-in-new-tab behavior.
- With MUI: `import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'` and `<Button component={Link} to="...">`.
